Package org.hd.d.TRVmodel.hg

Record Class HGTRVHPMModelParameterised.ModelParameters

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
org.hd.d.TRVmodel.hg.HGTRVHPMModelParameterised.ModelParameters
Record Components:
doorsPerInternalWall - was 0.5 in the original page calcs (but 1 in the text); expected to be in range [0,1], must be finite and positive
correctCoPForFlowVsMW - if true then correct CoP flow temperature (original page implies false)
roomsAlternatingABAB - if true then arrange rooms to maximise internal heat transfer/loss else arrange so as to minimise heat loss (original page implies true)
externalAirTemperatureC - external air temperature, degrees C; (original page has -3°C)
Enclosing class:
HGTRVHPMModelParameterised
public static record HGTRVHPMModelParameterised.ModelParameters(double doorsPerInternalWall, boolean correctCoPForFlowVsMW, boolean roomsAlternatingABAB, double externalAirTemperatureC) extends Record
Parameters for this version of the model. Defaults should yield the same
